<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天， 哈提抬起了他的鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们走吧！”他大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他和他的三个儿子出发了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大象向不同的方向行进。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们到了村民的田地，行进了好几天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们踩坏了草地、庄稼、工具和他们发现的其他任何东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>刚开始，别的森林动物远远地看着大象们行进。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后来，鸟们飞到森林上空传播消息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“食物！每个动物都能吃的食物！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，成群的鹿、猪和豪猪加入了大象的队伍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都开始吃剩下的庄稼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁来了，找到了一些好吃的根。“好吃！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>别的动物撞倒大麦，从蓄水池里喝水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鸟们飞下来吃种子和谷粒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蟒蛇卡阿爬进了山谷，猴子们吓得跑开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡阿也饿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大象在田地里不停地走来走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，村庄里的人们就饿得绝望了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有庄稼了。”一个村民说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须在森林中寻找食物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一群人进入森林寻找坚果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，有着明亮眼睛的影子们吓了他们一跳，他们跑了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124408</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雨季来临时，四头大象在田地里完成了他们的任务。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们开始向村民们的小屋走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在他们在做什么？”巴希拉问毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们要把小屋的屋顶掀下来。”毛克利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大多数村民已经离开去寻找新家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在剩下的人也该走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个月后，毛克利和巴希拉回到了村庄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里长满了草和密密的杂草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>六个月后，他们俩又回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，森林已经恢复了生机。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这正是我想象的，巴希拉。”毛克利小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>野生森林吞没了人类村庄的所有痕迹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大象行进后，毛克利回到了狼洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他找到一个方法惩罚残忍的村民们 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>根据森林法则，这个惩罚解决了所有的问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，毛克利既不安又不开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不觉得饿，也几乎睡不着觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我怎么了？”他很好奇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，天气很热，毛克利正在河里玩儿水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他渴望逃跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿过森林，从一棵树跳到另一棵树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑了一个下午，唱歌、游泳和打猎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他发现自己身处森林中一个陌生的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在一个村庄外的沼泽地附近，他听见几只狗在叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人类的村庄！”毛克利想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他好奇地向狗叫的声音走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们在小屋前走来走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利像狼一样咆哮，它们立刻不叫了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，一个女人走到门口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她戴着铜手镯，头发有点灰色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁在那儿？”她喊道。她吓得声音颤抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是另一只豺狼吗？”她问狗们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他仔细看着她时，毛克利觉得自己也开始发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个女人看上去有点老了，但他知道她的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>事实上，他很清楚！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“麦苏雅？”他大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从自己一直躲着的高草里走了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那女人吓了一跳，把手放在胸口上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿图，是你吗？我的儿子？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>